                    <p class="right"><span class="box box_yellow">행사중</span></p>
                </li>
                <li class="half mr_6p">
                    <p class="left color">상품 가격</p>
                    <p class="right">999,999</p>
                </li>
                <li class="half">
                    <p class="left color">포스 가격</p>
